OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773828292
OL,3,CGlasgow Central station partially
OL,4,Creopens after vape shop fire destroys
OL,5,Cbuilding
OL,7,FGlasgow Central has partially reopened
OL,8,Ften days after a fire ripped through a
OL,9,Fneighbouring building, devastating
OL,10,Fbusinesses and halting trains at
OL,11,FScotland's busiest railway station.
OL,13,FThe main part of the station had been
OL,14,Fclosed since Sunday, March 8, after
OL,15,Fthe fire destroyed much of the Union
OL,16,FCorner building.
OL,18,FPlatforms seven to 15 on the west side
OL,19,Fhigher level of the station resumed
OL,20,Foperating on Wednesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
