OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773828292
OL,3,CGlasgow Central station partially
OL,4,Creopens after vape shop fire destroys
OL,5,Cbuilding
OL,7,FNetwork Rail said the partial
OL,8,Freopening will mean there will be
OL,9,Freduced capacity and urged passengers
OL,10,Fto check their journey times before
OL,11,Ftravelling.
OL,13,FServices operating between the station
OL,14,Fand Ayr, Paisley Gilmour Street,
OL,15,FKilwinning, Gourock, Kilmarnock, East
OL,16,FKilbride and Carlisle have resumed,
OL,17,Fthough some will operate at reduced
OL,18,Fcapacity.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
