OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773828292
OL,3,CGlasgow Central station partially
OL,4,Creopens after vape shop fire destroys
OL,5,Cbuilding
OL,7,FDavid Ross, ScotRail chief operating
OL,8,Fofficer, said: "I am very pleased we
OL,9,Fwill be able to welcome customers back
OL,10,Fto Glasgow Central high level
OL,11,Ffollowing the partial reopening of the
OL,12,Fstation from Wednesday.
OL,14,F"We realise the closure is causing
OL,15,Fsignificant disruption for our
OL,16,Fcustomers, and we're very sorry for
OL,17,Fthe impact it is still having on
OL,18,Fjourneys."
OL,26,@pD@POUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
