PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773828292
OL,3,CGlasgow Central station partially
OL,4,Creopens after vape shop fire destroys
OL,5,Cbuilding
OL,7,FPassengers have been told the station
OL,8,Fwill "look different", with barriers
OL,9,Fand signage marking the exclusion zone
OL,10,Fand facilities and shops closed, and
OL,11,Fstaff will be on hand to offer advice.
OL,13,FGlasgow City Council said it is in the
OL,14,Finterests of public safety to demolish
OL,15,Fwhat remains of the "very unstable"
OL,16,FVictorian building which was ravaged
OL,17,Fby the fire.
OL,19,FDemolition experts have been working
OL,20,Fto safely bring down parts of the
OL,21,Fremaining structure.
OL,26,@pD@FOUpD@UO]wD@UOUwD@cO]
