PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773828292
OL,3,CGlasgow Central station partially
OL,4,Creopens after vape shop fire destroys
OL,5,Cbuilding
OL,7,FThe fire began in a vape shop in Union
OL,8,FStreet and spread through the building
OL,9,Fand around the corner, with only the
OL,10,Ffacade of the building at the junction
OL,11,Fwith Gordon Street left standing.
OL,13,FScotRail said stringent safety checks
OL,14,Fhad been carried out before the
OL,15,Fpartial reopening.
OL,17,FServices from the smaller low-level
OL,18,Fstation, which runs services to
OL,19,FBalloch, Milngavie, Motherwell and
OL,20,FCumbernauld, resumed last Wednesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
